values:
What is up people who still use this.  It has been almost been a year and a half since I last updated.  If you guys remember me give a holla.  But alas I must go hinse forth to work.

  Peace

Sorry to say I will not be making the trip this weekend because of complications here at the squadron.  So the next available chance for me will be in August after I graduate from here and go to my base first.  Sorry that I can't make it but I mean it I will be up there in August.
  Peace Out!

Sorry I have been very, very, very busy.  But aside from that I am having a great time at least on the weekends here.  Oh and I have some great news....I am coming up there 4th of July weekend.  So expect me Saturday July 1st till the 4th when I fly back.  Well I have to go.  I'll talk to you guys later.  Peace Out!

What up world?  Been a while since I updated.  Not too much happening here except I will finally start learning about what I will do for my job.  I am really excited!!  I still don't know when I graduate....they think it might be in late July now...but I really don't know.  I feel like I have been gone forever when I have only been gone for 4 months now.  Oh well I need to go study for my Test tomorrow.  

  Peace Out!

Ok time for a quick update.  So far school is not stressful but I know it will be soon.  I wake up at 4am and go to school until 3pm, after that I get back to the squadron and do a 4 mile run, sit ups, and push ups.  Then I get the rest of the day off.  At the moment I know that I am going to be here for at least 9 months.  The only good thing is I have my own dorm and I get the weekends off.  =)

  Aight I will talk to you guys later.  Peace Out!

Well to make this short and simple, yes I have made it to Tech School.  Lets see last 7 weeks have been hell.  I will go more in detail later.

  Peace Out!

Yesterday's party was off the hook!!  I am really happy on the turn out of the party.  I especially loved the toast you guys gave me and how you all told funny stories that had to do with me.....I almost shed some tears.  I am at a lose for words.  But I will miss all of you very much.  I will also miss those who weren't there.  Wow 5 days!!

Well if you will excuse me I am going to get ready to see Rent with Joe and Glinda.

Yesterday....well this morning I saw Harry Potter 4.  That movie was sooo awsome!  I think that they are getting better and better.  It was funny seeing the people react when Harry cursed.  Funny stuff.

  Anyways after the movie's went to Waffle House and talked with Aaron for about 2 hours.  I am very proud of him for trying to get out of this Sara situation.  But I am jealous that he can hang out and talk with his ex.  I wish it could be that easy for me but some of my ex's, on the other hand I know how some of them are and I really don't give a shit anymore.  It is sad that it had to be this way with some of them, but it just makes me angry that they would hide shit from me, when I don't give a rat's ass anymore.  Well that will end my rant, oh and this isn't pointed at one person but a couple of people.

  Well let me see.  I have only 10 days left!!  =)  I am really excited and can't wait to leave.  I will miss all of you!

Yeah I think that will do for now.

Long time no see people.  I have had no time what so ever to be online.  Lets me see I am jobless as of right now and I have 17 days left until I am gone.  =)  I got a sign on bonus with the Air Force for 10 Grand...but I will not touch it, it is in savings right now.  

  I really can't wait to leave cause I will be on my own officially.  I am a little scared but at the same time I want/need to do this.  I will miss all of you guys and some of you I will see in about August or September next year.  But if you want me to write you guys send me your address and I will give you a shout out from Texas.

  Aight peep's see ya later!

Everyone don't worry about my last entry I was not having a good week at all.  I am doing really good.

  My weekend was sooooooo AWESOME!!  First at work Friday I had a mystery shopper and I ended up getting a 93, so the big guy congratulated me and said that I was going to the McDonald's competition.  So Saturday I went to the competition (It put all the best workers from 10 different stores making a quote "Super McDonald's".....Sam said that)  I got my results today and I came in first in my area which was Order Taker for Drive Thru.  So now the people who won in there area's are now going to compete against Corporate McDonald's for a shot at 500 Dollars, for each person.

  Also Saturday night was sooooooooo much fun.  It was Joe's birthday and well I really don't remember too much of it.  I don't get drunk very ofter, but I did promise him that would at his party.  I did regret it Sunday morning but it was a fun night.  But I found out that I am a very emotional drunk.  I started to cry when Aaron left the room cause I thought that I made him angry and he left, and then 5 minutes later I was angry at Brad D. for not being drunk like I was.

Anyway it is about time that I head to bed for I worked 11 hours today and I open tomorrow.  So Good Night Everyone!!

Peek A Boo.......I See You!

Yeah lets see I have been workin like a crazy person.  I really don't have that much of a social life anymore.  I go to work and I go home that is about it.

I really hate my life right now.

Yes I actually have to weekend off!  They have made me an official opener.  So everyday just about I work from 4:30am till about 2:00pm

  Needless to say I haven't done a whole lot this week.  Work yesterday was say that I should not go in the military and I could be a manager in a couple of weeks......which I kindly say no thanks,  Arby's tried that with me too.  Well 2 days ago all the managers had a meeting and I ran the store with one manager who was in the back doing paper work the whole time.  I opened yesterday without a manager cause they gave me a key to the store.

  Sometime I hate that my life right now revolves around work.....It sucks.  Oh well less than 3 months  =)

Thing today got out of hand at work.  Two people on front counter almost got in a fight.  I had to break them up before it got worse, that and also there were little children around.  (they didn't need to hear all the stuff they had to say)

Tomorrow instead of working 9-5pm. I am now working 4:30-1:30pm.  (Covering for a friend, she owes me one)

Yesterday was fun went to the movies with Ryan, Joe, Aaron, and Sophia.  Sky High was kick ass, and it put me in a really good mood.

I hope that Aaron get better though.......poor guy.

Mon- OFF!
Tue- 4:30-1:30pm.
Wed- 6-3pm.
Thur- 4:30-1:30pm.
Fri- 9-5pm.
Sat- OFF!
Sun- 7-2pm.

OMFG, OMFG!  I only work 7 hours Sunday.

Anywho I'm off to wreak more havoc!!  =)

Lunch Time!

Taken from so many others.

1. Reply with your name and I will write something random about you.
2. I will then tell you what song/movie reminds me of you.
3. I will pick a flavor of jello to wrestle with you in.
4. I will say something that only makes sense to you and me.
5. I will tell you my first memory of you.
6. I will tell you what color you remind me of.
7. I'll then ask you something that I've always wondered about you.
8. If I do this for you, you must post this on your LJ. (and be prepared to answer the question I ask in #7)

I just got pulled into a lot of Drama.  Errrrrrr I hate Drama.  =(

Ok so one night I decide to hang out with some people from work.  I go to Mike's house and meet up with Taco and Wade, they are just chillin, talkin, and having a good time.  They want me to drink and I say "naw I'm good".  Later on they decide hey lets go to a bar I figured I would be the driver for them since none of them were fit to (except, maybe Taco).  I go there and I end up drinking two drinks (not harmful, didn't even have a buzz)  Well that was the end of the night for me and I went home.  Well today apparently Mike is gay.....so he was trying to get me drunk and have his way with me, so when I said no to getting drunk and staying longer, he went for Wade who told me that Taco had to keep Mike away from him.  Basically he was sleeping and Mike tried taking him to the other bedroom.

Anyway it just made my brain hurt today.  I don't think I will be hanging out with him anymore.

I need to get online more.

Yep I have gone a week with out spiking my hair.  And for the most part people didn't like me with my hair down.  They said that it wasn't me without the spikes.  Today people at work kept asking if I was going to spike my hair again.  So I have put my hair back up.  Oh yeah  Schedule Time!  =)

Mon- OFF!
Tue- 4:30- 1:30pm
Wed- OFF!
Thur- 8-4pm
Fri- 9-5pm
Sat- 6-2pm
Sun- 7-4pm

So yeah umm....that is it.  Peace Out!

This was an awsome weekend and Monday!  I spent Friday and Saturday at Ashton's house and then Sunday I chilled over at Stephanie's house.  But Monday had to be the best at Warp Tour!  Saw soo many good bands.  There was MxPx, Thrice, Transplants, Offsping, and many more.  My favorite is between Transplants and Thrice.  It was soo hot all day and it finally rained when Fall Out Boy played.  During Offspring I got involved in a moshpit, fun except for being kicked and punched in the face.  Other than that I had a blast.

  On another note I got my job for the Air Force and I am leaving November 29!  Yay!  =)

  I have today and only today off Oh Well.  I am going to stay out of the sun for a while (sun burn and all).

  Hope to hear from you guys soon and possibly hang out before I leave.

Work was fucking bullshit today (sorry for the language)!!  I have never seen things so messed up in my life.  Lets just say we were slammed to hell All Day Long.

  Anyways on a lighter note, someone who I have had a crush on for 6 years now just told me yesterday that she has had a crush on me since 8th grade.  That had to be one of the weirdest things that has happened recently.  So I am really happy right now!!  =)

  Wedding Crashers is Awsome.

  Ok nothing else at the moment.......shower time!

Today was very productive.  Went and turned in my tags for the Volvo (so it isn't coming back)  Went with Ryan to the Ford dealership and am now looking into a new car.  Pimp Ass!  Then went to the DMV again cause I didn't turn them in this morning.  Met Steve there and we got lost in Moncks Corner for a while.  After that got Little Caesars and took it back to Ryan's to eat....finally.

Anywho I can't wait for this weekend!!!

Oh and I got paid today!

Peace Out!
SHAW NAW NAW NAW,  SHAW NAW NAW NAW,  HEY HEY HEY SNOOP DOGG!!

Well not too much happening in my life.  Same old running a muck with people I know and don't know.  Been working a lot and umm.....that is about it.

Schedule Time!!

Mon- OFF!

Thur- 8-4pm.

Sun- 10-6pm.

What up people?  Long time no talk.  Umm......lets see.  Life can hand you a shitty deal at times but I realize why the fuck (excuse my french) should I be depressed.  Like for instance I lost my job but went and didn't mope around I got a better job.  My car just died (officially) but I am sure I will get a better car.  If not for a while I will do just fine.

  Just thought I would tell how a feel at the moment, but when you see me I will be the same old Drew!!  Hope to see any of you soon.

Love to all,
      Me! :)

Wed- 8-4pm
Thur- Off!
Fri- 8-4pm

Work was interesting.  Everyone was nice and I got the hang of it real quick.  Not much to say though, tired.

G'night!

Ok so things just got better.  I went for the job interview at McDonald's and well it wasn't really an interview.  I walked in and Andy came up to me handed me two shirts and told me to fill out all my info down.  So I start work tomorrow and I am working from 8-4pm. and am getting 6 dollars an hour.  =)

  He also said that he would give me hours!!

  Also my Dad showed up in town......very odd.  So he took me and bought me new pants and shoes for work.  Well I think I will go.

Peace Out!!

Ok, ok, ok.  A couple of days ago I had one weird day.  First off I was climbing up on to one of the shelves to get some cups and when I jumped down my right shoe blew up!  Then later that day I was grabbing soda from my manager's car and my pants ripped down the crotch area.  Yeah I thought it was funny so I figured I would share with part of the world.

  Today was cool, went to work....yada, yada, yada.  After work I chilled at home until Joe got here and then Stephanie got here and we all went to Leni's house and played phase 10.  (I won, Yes!)  Finally Joe and I went cruising down the Summerville area.

Any who I am going to bed!

Peace Out!

HAPPY 4TH OF JULY!!  Well a year ago I didn't see how my life would be a year later.  Last year I was closing and I was better friends with some people.  I didn't think I would be here, but I think that my life is turning out better than planned.  I am glad that I have met some of my new friend's cause you guys are cool.  I can't wait to leave but I will miss you guys a lot.  =[  Oh well just thinking out loud.

Just got back from Sophia's apartment, it was really cool party.  (very relaxing)  =)

Any who G'night all!

I have to be up in a couple hours for work.....but I can't seem to fall asleep.  AHHHHHHH!

  I am toooo wired right now.

Strange shit always finds its way to me.  I went to answer the door today and and someone was here for Rita (my step dads ex).  So this person thinks that she lives here and that my step dad is dead.  I am really fucking confused right now.  I think I am going to go get some medicine for my headache.

Peace Out!

Bitches and Hoes
Bitches and Hoes

Some people need to find a nice park or a house, but I still don't see how horny you have to be to do it in the bathroom.  Trez, a guy I work with, found 2 people having sex.  He darted out of the bathroom and told everyone he seemed scared.  I laughed, and so did everyone else.  That was his first time catching that happening.  Anyways the new Steak Wrap and Peanut Butter Cup shake is Awsome!  Yesterday I played paintball....not too long though, I was wearing shorts and a t-shirt.  Well that is all for now.  TTFN!  ta ta for now!

Stephanie, I am really sorry about yesterday.  I feel like shit.  Sorry.

I think I need more sleep.  The past two days I have opened at 5:30 in the morning and then worked till 4 or 5.  I work like a manager but don't get paid like one.  Other than work I have been hangin out with Ryan, Joe, and Amanda S.  We all went to Little Caesars yesterday and saw "Guess Who".  The movie was really funny.  I need sleep but I don't want to go to bed so I think I will be an idiot and go hang out with my peeps, for rizal.

Today was good, I got to hang out with Sam.  We went bowling and went back to his house and mixed up some phat beats yo.

  I then went with Joe and Brad and looked at a play they are doing in October.  We are going to try out for it and hopefully we will get selected.  (I need to brush up on my acting a little)

"Sex is the Attic"

  Today I worked all day until about 7:30pm.  There was an old lady about 70 something, her car wasn't working cause it overheated and she didn't have any water.  So I went out to her car and helped her out.  I told her that I didn't want a reward for helping but she used her power of seniority over me.  Damn the elderly!!  Anyways right after that I went and saw Cory at Hess, he then offered me his sausage.....I mean a hotdog.  Stephanie showed up and we all just talked for a while.  After that I went home for a little until I got a call on my phone.  Stephanie wanted to hang out and I was like sure (even though we already planned on doing that).  I said we should pick up Joe, so we did.  We went back to Hess and helped then close by keeping customers away.  Finally went to Joe's and watched Idol Hands, I am not done with it but I will finish it later.

  *side note*  I LOVE YOU GUYS!!

  Peace Out!

Family Guy was awsome!!  American Dad was too!

  Work was ok, a lot of shit happened and I ended up being the only backline person for lunch. (fun)  Chilled at home for the rest of today.  I love the days that are relaxing after work.

Yay!!  I was a manager today with the keys to the store and everything.  I ran reports and ran around like mad for about an hour.  I could get used to power like that.  I am really hyper so I think I will go outside and flip for a little!!  =)

Peace Out!

  Yay!! hung out with Ashton today.....I miss her.  She needs to be down more often.

*side note* entry 200 woot woot!

Yesterday was fun.  I didn't have work so I chilled at home.  At about 7:30 I went with Joe and we went to Craig's and watched Sea Lab and Aqua Teen.  (very pimp)  After that we went and hung out with Stephanie for a while.  I just got off work and now I am typing on my computer.  Life is sooooo interesting.

  I want a pet!

Yesterday has got to be one of the weirdest days that I have had in a while.  Went to work , blah blah blah, and a couple hours later I was home.  Talk with Ryan online he then came and got me.  We didn't know what we were doing but as we were driving down the road we saw Sean Johnson, no fucking lie!  We both turned and was like was that Sean.  We turned around and met up with him.  We went to his house and then picked up Joe.  Went to the Arcade to bother Steve and play some DDR.  After that we went to the parking lot and met up with Bernie and Emily (haven't seen them in a while so that was cool).  Finally went went driving everywhere and met up with Kat in the Target parking lot, where we all sat down and talked for a while.  Ryan dropped me off and I then played some Halo and went to bed.
  Now about today......choices.

Today was a very good day at work! =)  Even though I had to do maintenance I made it fun.  Today I moved the TV out to the front line and I put in the fish video.  We watched it like 6 times.  We all had a blast, I was in Drive Thru with Joe (first time ever) and we created chaos.  We were all singing and yelling and it was just fun!

Now I am hyper as hell!!!  I need to get out somehow.

Save my mind!

ERRRRR!  I hate when people are fake to your face and you can tell that they are being fake.  It just really erks me that they have the audacity to do that.  If there is a problem with me then tell me,don't be an asshole about it.  Or just don't bother being my friend.  (this is not pointed at one person but a few people)

Yesterday was cool went down town with Joe and Amanda to go to Stephanie's Birthday lunch thing.  That was really fun.  After they left Joe, Amanda, and me went to a bunch of comic book stores!  I love reading comics!  We were heading towards the beach but I was rushed with a sudden sickness, which was not cool, so I went home and passed out on my couch.  Woke up this morning and felt a little better.  Got off work at 5:30 and have been chillin at home ever since.
